 c煤bico.
 (
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$
\backslash
si{g/cm^3}$
\end_layout

\end_inset

).(Un gramo es la masa que corresponde 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

1
\backslash
si{cm^3}
\end_layout

\end_inset

