\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{1}=\dfrac{\Delta_{1}m}{\Delta_{1}x}\inline\text{\label{eq:ec7}}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
El cociente incremental de la ecuaci贸n (
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
